  "text": "The Event-B computational model is that of a state machine (see Listing 5.2). Built-in to the Event-B [CITATION_1] modeling language used by Rodin is a methodology for traversing various levels of abstraction: What is particularly attractive about the Rodin tool is this ability to carry formal requirements from the specification level all the way through to its implementation.",
